review_blob: Aroma: Grainy, wheaty... Appearance: Pale yellow, with a thin white head... Taste: Wheaty, light bitterness... Palate: average carbonation, medium body... Not a bad drink, except I only managed to drink 3/4s of my glass until i spilt the rest all over my girlfriend.

Aroma: Citrus and Corn... Appearance: Clear pale yellow with a fine withe head... Taste: Light bitterness... Palate: Watery, light body...  Not a beer to sit and sip on, its a beer to drink fast and get really really drunk off of.
